<bibRefCitation id="EFF04B5826399C32A0343185FDE71702" author="Gagnepain, F." box="[323,528,1523,1550]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" pagination="18 - 25" refId="ref4364" refString="Gagnepain, F. (1908) Burmanniacees. In: Lecomte, H. &amp; Gagnepain, F. (Eds.) Flore generale de l'Indo-Chine, vol. 6. Masson &amp; Cie, Paris, pp. 18 - 25." type="book chapter" year="1908">Gagnepain (1908)</bibRefCitation>
