<bibRefCitation id="EFF04B5826399C32A3263261FCC3173E" author="Yudina, S. V. &amp; Kocyan, A. &amp; Truong, B. V. &amp; Vislobokov, N. A. &amp; Lyskov, D. F. &amp; Nuraliev, M. S. &amp; Remizowa, M. V." box="[593,820,1559,1586]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" pagination="849276" refId="ref5798" refString="Yudina, S. V., Kocyan, A., Truong, B. V., Vislobokov, N. A., Lyskov, D. F., Nuraliev, M. S. &amp; Remizowa, M. V. (2022) Structure and development of flowers and inflorescences in Burmannia (Burmanniaceae, Dioscoreales). Frontiers in Plant Science 13: 849276. https: // doi. org / 10.3389 / fpls. 2022.849276" type="journal article" year="2022">
Yudina 
<emphasis id="B915EABB26399C32A3D0326EFD28173D" box="[679,735,1559,1585]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">et al.</emphasis>
(2022)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C37B652226399C33A1FF322AFA5C138D" lastPageId="7" lastPageNumber="68" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" type="key">
<keyStep id="30952E0C26399C32A1FF322AFA5C1782" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">
<paragraph id="8BDE36A926399C32A1FF322AFA5C177D" blockId="6.[136,1452,1628,2082]" box="[136,1451,1628,1650]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">
<keyLead id="3090959C26399C32A1FF322AFA5C177D" box="[136,1451,1628,1650]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">1. Plant chlorophyllous (with green leaves and stem)............................................................................................................................2</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDE36A926399C32A1FF320FFA5C1782" blockId="6.[136,1452,1628,2082]" box="[136,1451,1657,1679]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">
<keyLead id="3090959C26399C32A1FF320FFA5C1782" box="[136,1451,1657,1679]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">- Plant apparently achlorophyllous (lacking green coloration in all plant parts)..................................................................................8</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep id="30952E0C26399C32A1FF32E0FA5C17CB" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">
<paragraph id="8BDE36A926399C32A1FF32E0FA5D17A7" blockId="6.[136,1452,1628,2082]" box="[136,1450,1685,1707]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">
<keyLead id="3090959C26399C32A1FF32E0FA5D17A7" box="[136,1450,1685,1707]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">
2. Plant robust, perennial, with at least some leaves longer than 
<quantity id="4C999B4C26399C32A26832E0FCB917A7" box="[799,846,1686,1707]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" unit="cm" value="3.0">3 cm</quantity>
and wider than 
<quantity id="4C999B4C26399C32A29E32E0FBDD17A7" box="[1001,1066,1686,1707]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" unit="cm" value="0.3">0.3 cm</quantity>
.............................................. 
<taxonomicName id="4C614D2A26399C32A43632E0FA5D17A7" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" box="[1345,1450,1685,1707]" class="Liliopsida" family="Burmanniaceae" genus="Burmannia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Dioscoreales" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="disticha">
<emphasis id="B915EABB26399C32A43632E0FA5D17A7" bold="true" box="[1345,1450,1685,1707]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">B. disticha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDE36A926399C32A1FF32C5FA5C17CB" blockId="6.[136,1452,1628,2082]" box="[136,1451,1714,1736]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">
<keyLead id="3090959C26399C32A1FF32C5FA5C17CB" box="[136,1451,1714,1736]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">
- Plant delicate, annual, with leaves up to 
